"Add a recovery email to retain access when single-sign on is not available. "
"Go to {link_start}your Account Settings{link_end}."
msgstr ""
"Add a recovery email to retain access when single-sign on is not available. "
"Go to {link_start}your Account Settings{link_end}."

#: common/djangoapps/student/views/management.py:580
#, python-brace-format
