msgstr "ཞབས་ཞུའི་རྣམ་གྲངས་དང་ཁྲིམས་མཐུན་སྒྲིག་གཞི།"

#: openedx/core/djangoapps/user_authn/views/registration_form.py:1022
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"I agree to the {platform_name} "
"{terms_of_service_link_start}{terms_of_service}{terms_of_service_link_end}"
